summary: High quality ENB preset with DOF, sweet FX for ENB 0.229, compatibile with CTD and Memory patch ENBoost
descriptionHtml:
Good Vision ENB
Video on YouTube
[youtube]qaInEaEJRfo[/youtube]

 Download the ENB 0.229 binary first ! 

Good Vision ENB is the high quality preset for ENB mod with very good performance and looking. 
INSTALATION


 1. Deactivate AA / SSAO in game settings AND/OR over videodriver

2. Copy all files files from my ENB to Skyrim main folder

3. Copy d3d9.dll by Boris Vorontsov to Skyrim main folder

My PC:
-Intel Pentium Dual Core 2.5GHZ
-ATI Radeon Asus HD5770 1 GB DDR5 CU Core
-3GB DDR2 RAM

Thanks for:
Boris Vorntsov for create ENB mod
